About this item

  • ENHANCED PERFORMANCE AND DURABILITY - The Powerstrike Bat Cricket is designed with heavy-duty plastic, ensuring superior durability and performance. It's an ideal hard plastic cricket bat for serious and recreational players
  • FULL-SIZE ADULT BAT - Experience tournament standard quality with this full-size adult bat. Perfect for those intense gully cricket games or a friendly match. Definitely a must-have among your collection of cricket bats
  • EXCEPTIONAL FOR PRO AND LEAGUE PLAY - Built with sophisticated aesthetics and functionality, our unique power tennis cricket bat ensures a comfortable grip for expert handling. Perfect for thriving in professional and recreational cricket action
  • DURABLE MATERIAL - Unlike typical plastic cricket bat, this bat is made with a hard plastic exterior and fiber interior, providing enhanced performance without compromising on durability. This bat plastic is designed for optimum play
  • PREMIUM QUALITY - Our hard tennis cricket bat promises long-term durability and performance. Crafted from premium leather, it offers unique balance and power. This plastic bat full size is indeed a game-changer in the field of cricket
